---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="DIY Guides & Tutorials | CalcForDIY"
  description="Read our step-by-step guides and tutorials for home improvement, landscaping, and DIY projects."
>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
    <a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-600">Home</a>
    <span>/</span>
    <span>Guides</span>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">DIY Guides & Tutorials</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">Step-by-step instructions to help you plan your materials perfectly.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    <a href="/guides/how-much-mulch-for-garden-beds" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How Much Mulch Do I Need for Garden Beds?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Learn exactly how to calculate the amount of mulch you need for your garden beds, including measuring and depth recommendations.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/guides/soil-4x8-raised-bed" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How Much Soil to Fill a 4x8 Raised Bed?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">A practical breakdown of exactly how many bags or cubic yards you need to fill the most popular raised bed size, based on different depths.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/guides/how-many-bags-of-grout-for-tile-shower" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How Many Bags of Grout for a Tile Shower?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Learn how tile size and joint width affect your coverage, and calculate exactly how much material you need.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/guides/how-many-studs-for-a-wall" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How Many Studs Do I Need for a Wall?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Learn exactly how to calculate the number of studs needed for a wall, including the math for corners, doors, windows, and standard waste factors.</p>
    </a>
    <!-- Future guides will go here -->
  </div>
</Layout>
